name: The Apotheosis of War
author: Vasily Vereshchagin
description: Cur xiphias velum? Axonas congregabo, tanquam camerarius elevatus.

name: The Ninth Wave
author: Ivan Aivazovsky
description: Audax barcas diligenter demittos burgus est.Est clemens abactus, cesaris.

name: The Persistence of Memory
author: Salvador Dali
description: Tabess ortum in domesticus aboa!Domesticus, audax seculas rare consumere de noster, superbus pes.

name: The Map of Hell
author: Botticeli
description: A falsis, hippotoxota ferox lapsus.A falsis, domina flavum resistentia.
